      value: 'Saw off the rib bones as fast as you can! Watch the rib bones as they
        light up in a random order, then match the sequence by  <b>clicking</b> the
        bones in the correct order using the mouse. After each correct click, fill
        the meter by keeping the saw icon inside the moving green zone. Tap <b>E</b>
        to raise the saw icon or do nothing to let it fall. Fill the meter completely
        to win! '
